Race.SpecificTitle: Town of Grand Coteau -- 15.00 Mills - M&BOA - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Town of Grand Coteau, State of Louisiana (the "Town"), levy a fifteen (15.00) mills tax on all the property subject to taxation in the Town for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2020 and ending with the year 2029 (an estimated $82,432.65 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the Tax for an entire year), for the purpose of acquiring, construction, improving, maintaining and operating fire protection and equipment?
